metadata.name: 1001 Nights
metadata.description:
A soft breeze lifts the curtain as the pale moonlight brightens up the room. Sitting on a table is an old lamp, reminding us of a distant tale where a genie is ready to enter the scene and work their magic...
Make a wish !
